patthana23.9:1.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naācayagāmiṁ dhammaṁ paccayā kusalo ācayagāmī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.9:2.1_0: Nakusalaṁ naapacayagāmiṁ dhammaṁ paccayā kusalo apacayagāmī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.9:3.1_0: Nakusalaṁ nanevācayagāmināpacayagāmiṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca abyākato nevācayagāmināpacayagāmī dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
